OL,3,CBristol residents protest 'liveable
OL,4,Cneighbourhood' plans
OL,6,FResidents in South Bristol have taken
OL,7,Fto the streets to show their anger
OL,8,Fover a proposed 'Liveable
OL,9,FNeighbourhood' in Southville,
OL,10,FTotterdown and Bedminster.
OL,12,FThe scheme would see a number of roads
OL,13,Fin the BS3 area blocked off to traffic
OL,14,Fwith bollards and planters being
OL,15,Finstalled.
OL,17,FBristol City Council claims it would
OL,18,F"create a better balance" between how
OL,19,Fstreets are used, making them safer,
OL,20,Fquieter and less polluted.
