OL,6,FThe authority also said their aim is
OL,7,Fto work with communities to design
OL,8,Fareas that will encourage people to
OL,9,Fwalk, cycle and wheel for shorter
OL,10,Fjourneys, whilst improving air quality
OL,11,Fand enhancing green spaces in South
OL,12,FBristol.
OL,14,FHowever, those opposing the plans
OL,15,Fclaim it will make their journeys
OL,16,Flonger.
OL,18,FThose against the plans marched to
OL,19,FCity Hall on Thursday 5th February,
OL,20,Fhighlighting their concerns over the
OL,21,Fproposals.
