OL,6,FAround 100 residents joined the march
OL,7,Fthrough Bristol, with one person
OL,8,Fdescribing the plan as "pointless".
OL,10,FShe saying: "The side roads are very
OL,11,Fquiet anyway, it will just divert the
OL,12,Ftraffic onto North Street which is
OL,13,Fbusy enough as it is."
OL,15,FAnother told ITV News: "I see a lot of
OL,16,Fpeople who are going to really
OL,17,Fstruggle with the restrictions and I
OL,18,Fdon't see a solution. We don't have a
OL,19,Fproblem in our neighbour that this
OL,20,Fthing addresses.
