OL,3,CBristol residents protest 'liveable
OL,4,Cneighbourhood' plans
OL,6,F"They say it's just a longer route
OL,7,Faround but they don't actually care
OL,8,Fthat for a disabled person the longer
OL,9,Froute means more pain and more
OL,10,Ffatigue," She added.
OL,12,F"We basically feel like we are living
OL,13,Fin an open prison and we are trapped
OL,14,Fin our homes."
OL,16,FMore than 3,000 people have now signed
OL,17,Fa petition against the South Bristol
OL,18,FLiveable Neighbourhood.
OL,20,FBristol City Council has been
OL,21,Fapproached for a comment.
